{"id":"zaavan","term":"Zaavan","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Terror, one of the “dukes of Edom” (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:27\">Gen. 36:27</a>); called also Zavan (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 1:42\">1 Chr. 1:42</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 36:27","1 Chronicles 1:42"]}